sql:
SELECT client_name
FROM clients
WHERE client_id NOT IN (
    SELECT client_id
    FROM projects
);

external_knowledge:
Significant amount of ongoing tasks refers to more than 10 tasks;
Tech companies refer to those operating in the Technology industry;
Software-related projects include any project name containing the phrase "Software Development".

sql:
SELECT 
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM clients) AS total_clients,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM projects) AS total_projects;
